      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry; COU device is a derivative design sharing impeller topology and volute proportions. Fluid (porcine blood) is accepted analogue for human blood at these shear rates. Gap analysis identifies minor geometric differences (±5% impeller diameter); sensitivity study confirms RH insensitive to this variation. Relevance criterion met at Gradation 2."
