    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. Validation evidence supports use of the CFD model to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH predictions demonstrate sufficient accuracy (MAE 8.3%) against FDA benchmark data. Model credibility is sufficient for the intended regulatory submission.",
